title: Find Your New Home Here!
posting_body: ['Welcome Home to Callen', 'Welcome to Callen, where convenience, style and comfort meet!', 'Residents at Callen have the convenience of being centrally located with easy access to the freeway and Olympia, DuPont and Tacoma, while still being situated far enough from the main road to enjoy the peace and quiet of a secluded neighborhood.', 'Being just blocks away from shopping (Safeway, Wal-Mart, Costco, etc.)', 'makes running errands a breeze!', "Our spacious one and two bedroom floor plans offer everything you're looking for in an apartment home!", 'The kitchens come equipped with a full-sized refrigerator, self-cleaning oven, microwave, dishwasher, full-sized double sink with garbage disposal and a pantry.', 'Every apartment comes with a full-sized washer and dryer, plenty of storage space, cable hook-ups in each room, private patios or balconies and even vaulted ceilings in select apartment homes.', 'We at Callen take pride in our community and every patio or balcony faces our professionally landscaped and meticulously maintained grounds!', 'We would love to show you around our wonderful community and assist you in any way we can with helping you find your new home!', 'Give one of our leasing professionals a call and schedule your tour today!', 'Call Now:', 'show contact info', 'x 110', 'OR Text', '110', 'to', 'show contact info', 'to text our leasing team.', 'More unit details at:', '<URL>', 'This is a 1 Bedroom, 1 Bath, approximately 772 Sq.', 'Ft.', 'Features', '- Dishwasher', '- Fireplace - Gas', '- Linen Closet', '- Cable Ready', '- Vaulted Ceilings *', '- Pantry', '- Built-In Microwave', '- Private Patio/Balcony', '- Washer/Dryer Included', '*in select apartments', 'Community Amenities', '- EV Charging Stations', '- Gated Community', '- Clubhouse', '- On-Site Maintenance', '- Pet Park', '- Garages Available', '- Fitness Center', '- Package Receiving', '- Extra Storage Available', '- Spa', '- Swimming Pool', '- Playgrounds', 'Pet Policy', 'Pet friendly, contact for details.', 'Office Hours', 'Monday-Friday:8:30AM-5:30PM', 'Saturday:10:00AM-5:00PM', 'Callen', '1404 Brittany Ln NE, Lacey, WA, 98516', 'We do not accept Comprehensive Reusable Tenant Screening Reports as defined by and pursuant to RCW 59.18.', '1YvRhbTiS2']
